'''貝爾傳媒'''（{{lang-en|Bell Media}}；{{lang-fr|Bell Média}}）是[[加拿大|加拿大]]一家[[大眾媒體|大眾媒體]]企業，為[[加拿大貝爾|加拿大貝爾公司]]的一家子公司，旗下業務包括電視製作及廣播（資產包括[[CTV電視網|CTV電視網]]、[[CTV第二台|CTV第二台]]及[[Noovo|Noovo]]）、廣播電台、[[數碼媒體|數碼媒體]]及網站。

==歷史==
===前身===
[[加拿大貝爾|加拿大貝爾公司]]於2000年與《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》母公司木橋（{{lang|en|The Woodbridge Company}}）合組「貝爾環球傳媒」公司（{{lang|en|Bell Globemedia}}），並收購[[CTV電視網|CTV公司]]<ref>[http://www.cbc.ca/news/story/2000/02/25/bcectv000225.html BCE announces $2.3 billion bid for CTV] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/story/2000/02/25/bcectv000225.html |date=20200501102515 }}, CBC.ca, February 25, 2000 (modified November 11, 2000); accessed August 9, 2006</ref><ref>[http://www.crtc.gc.ca/eng/archive/2000/DB2000-747.htm Decision CRTC 2000-747] {{Wayback|url=http://www.crtc.gc.ca/eng/archive/2000/DB2000-747.htm |date=20200813031324 }}, Transfer of effective control of CTV Inc. to BCE Inc., ''CRTC'', December 7, 2000</ref>。貝爾持有該公司80%股份，餘下則歸木橋。貝爾環球傳媒則於2001年與[[可即可|可即可]]組成財團購入[[魁北克省|魁北克省]]的法語[[Noovo|四季電視網]]，兩間公司的持股量分別為40%和60%，交易於同年12月7日獲[[加拿大視訊委員會|加拿大視訊委員會]]（CRTC）批准<ref name="CCF-V">{{cite web|url=http://www.broadcasting-history.ca/listing_and_histories/v-network|title=V Network|website=History of Canadian Broadcasting|publisher=Canadian Communications Foundation|accessdate=2020-06-02|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203045942/http://broadcasting-history.ca/listing_and_histories/v-network|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

貝爾於2005年12月宣佈減持貝爾環球傳媒股份，8.5%股權售予木橋、20%股權售予多倫多星報集團、另外20%股權則售予安大略教師退休金計劃；貝爾繼續保留該公司20%股份。這項交易於2006年8月完成<ref>"[http://www.cnw.ca/en/releases/archive/August2006/30/c9716.html BGM Ownership Deal Closes] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnw.ca/en/releases/archive/August2006/30/c9716.html |date=20071202033123 }}", BGM press release, August 30, 2006</ref>。

2006年7月12日，[[Citytv|Citytv]]的母公司CHUM有限公司宣佈將旗下的廣播媒體出售予貝爾環球傳媒；後者原本打算保留{{lang|en|Citytv}}[[電視系統|系統]]，而將{{lang|en|[[CTV第二台|A-Channel]]}}以及其他資產轉售，以獲取CRTC批准交易<ref name=takeover>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/story/2006/07/12/chum-bell.html|title=Bell Globemedia makes $1.7B bid for CHUM|publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|加拿大廣播公司]]|date=2006-07-12|accessdate=2006-07-12|archive-date=2011-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110908083837/https://www.cbc.ca/news/story/2006/07/12/chum-bell.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。為了集資進行這宗交易，貝爾環球傳媒於2006年9月向既有股東出售額外股權，但貝爾沒有參與其中。交易過後，安大略教師退休金計劃持有的股權增至25%，而貝爾持有的股權則減至15%<ref>[http://www.newswire.ca/en/releases/archive/September2006/07/c3905.html Bell Globemedia Completes Financing to Pay for CHUM Limited Shares] {{Wayback|url=http://www.newswire.ca/en/releases/archive/September2006/07/c3905.html |date=20070930222027 }}, BGM press release, September 7, 2006</ref>；公司名稱遂於2007年改為「CTV環球傳媒」（{{lang|en|CTVglobemedia}}）。 

CRTC於2007年6月8日批准CTV環球傳媒收購CHUM。然而，Citytv當時全數五間直屬地區分台皆與當地的[[CTV電視網|CTV電視網]]直屬分台直接競爭，CRTC遂下令CTV環球傳媒放售Citytv以防媒體壟斷。CTV環球傳媒於同月11日宣佈保留A-Channel系統，並將五間Citytv地區分台售予[[羅渣士通訊集團|羅渣士通訊集團]]，交易作價為3億7500萬元<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.thestar.com/Business/article/224297 | title = Rogers buys Citytv stations | language =  | accessdate = 2007-06-12 | work = The Star | location = Toronto | first = Jim | last = Byers | date = June 12, 2007 | archive-date = 2007-06-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070614074910/http://www.thestar.com/Business/article/224297 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://micro.newswire.ca/release.cgi?rkey=1506113399&view=16336-0&Start=0 | title = Rogers Communications Inc, Official News Release: Rogers buys Citytv Stations | accessdate = 2007-08-18 | year = 2007 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130115104758/http://micro.newswire.ca/release.cgi?rkey=1506113399&view=16336-0&Start=0 | archivedate = 2013-01-15 }}</ref>。交易於同年9月28日獲CRTC批准，並於同年10月31日正式完成。（A-Channel於2008年易名為「A」，再於2011年易名為[[CTV第二台|CTV第二台]]。）

CTV環球傳媒其後放售非核心資產，當中包括於因面臨財困而於2007年12月申請進入債權保護的四季電視網<ref name="CCF-V"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/business/quebec-broadcaster-tqs-in-creditor-protection-1.641133|title=Quebec broadcaster TQS in creditor protection|publisher=CBC News|date=2007-12-18|accessdate=2020-06-02}}</ref>。Remstar於2008年收購四季電視網<ref>[https://www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/story/RTGAM.20080310.wtqs0310/BNStory/Business "Judge approves Remstar acquisition of TQS"], Report on Business, March 10, 2008.</ref>，並於2009年將之更名為「V」。

===近期發展===
貝爾於2010年9月宣佈再度購入CTV環球傳媒的所有廣播資產：貝爾打算以現金加股票方式向木橋、多倫多星報集團和安大略教師退休金計劃支付13億元，並承擔CTV環球傳媒的17億元欠債。貝爾亦計劃將其持有的部分《環球郵報》股權售回木橋，讓其取回該報的大多數操控權。交易當時預期於2011年4月完成<ref name="bell-pr-2010">{{cite web|url=http://www.newswire.ca/en/releases/archive/September2010/10/c8677.html|title=Bell to acquire 100% of Canada's No.1 media company CTV|publisher=CNW Group|author=Bell Canada|date=2010-09-10|accessdate=2010-09-10|archive-date=2010-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100913060021/http://www.newswire.ca/en/releases/archive/September2010/10/c8677.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但《環球郵報》股權交易無需CRTC批准，故早於2010年12月完成<ref name="globesale-2011">{{cite news|url=http://www.thestar.com/business/companies/article/915934--torstar-completes-first-stage-of-ctvglobemedia-sale|title=Torstar completes first stage of CTVglobemedia sale|work=Toronto Star|date=2011-01-04|accessdate=2011-01-09|archive-date=2012-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024004313/http://www.thestar.com/business/companies/article/915934--torstar-completes-first-stage-of-ctvglobemedia-sale|dead-url=no}}</ref>。CTV環球傳媒交易於2011年3月7日獲CRTC許可<ref>[http://www.crtc.gc.ca/eng/com100/2011/r110307.htm CRTC approves BCE’s purchase of CTVglobemedia] {{Wayback|url=http://www.crtc.gc.ca/eng/com100/2011/r110307.htm |date=20150305155104 }}, ''CRTC'', March 7, 2011</ref><ref>[http://www.crtc.gc.ca/eng/archive/2011/2011-163.htm Broadcasting Decision CRTC 2011-163] {{Wayback|url=http://www.crtc.gc.ca/eng/archive/2011/2011-163.htm |date=20210419114253 }}, Change in effective control of CTVglobemedia Inc.'s licensed broadcasting subsidiaries, ''CRTC'', March 7, 2011</ref>，並於同年4月1日完成，貝爾傳媒遂告成立<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ctv.ca/CTVNews/TopStories/20110307/crtc-approves-ctvglobemedia-purchase-by-bce-110307/ |title=CRTC approves BCE's purchase of CTVglobemedia |accessdate=2016-06-11 |archive-date=2011-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629044310/http://www.ctv.ca/CTVNews/TopStories/20110307/crtc-approves-ctvglobemedia-purchase-by-bce-110307/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年3月16日，貝爾宣佈斥資33億8千萬元收購總部位於[[蒙特婁|蒙特婁]]的星芒傳媒（{{lang|en|Astral Media}}），並將其廣播資產歸入貝爾傳媒。貝爾計劃憑籍星芒傳媒持有的電影網絡（{{lang|en|The Movie Network}}）以及加拿大版[[HBO|HBO]]頻道股權來增强其收費電視業務，以抗衡[[Netflix|Netflix]]等串流媒體所帶來的競爭；此外貝爾亦期望透過星芒傳媒持有的法語廣播媒體擴展在[[魁北克省|魁北克省]]的市場佔有率<ref name=fp-snaps>{{cite web|last=Sturgeon|first=Jamie|title=Bell snaps up Astral Media for $3.38-billion|url=http://business.financialpost.com/2012/03/16/bce-snaps-up-astral-media-for-3-38-billion/|publisher=Financial Post|accessdate=29 April 2012|archive-date=2014-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140421111307/http://business.financialpost.com/2012/03/16/bce-snaps-up-astral-media-for-3-38-billion/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。CRTC有感收購星芒傳媒後的貝爾在加拿大廣播市場佔有過多份率，故於2012年10月否決這宗交易。

貝爾和星芒隨後展開新一輪磋商，並同意將星芒的大部分英語電視頻道售予其他集團（如[[康力斯娛樂|康力斯娛樂]]），以消除CRTC的顧慮<ref name=gandm-confirmedtalks>{{cite news|title=Astral confirms talks with BCE to resurrect takeover deal|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/globe-investor/astral-confirms-talks-with-bce-to-resurrect-takeover-deal/article5369161/|publisher=The Globe and Mail|accessdate=17 November 2012|location=Toronto|date=16 November 2012|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125235500/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/globe-investor/astral-confirms-talks-with-bce-to-resurrect-takeover-deal/article5369161/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=crtc-bellastral-denied>{{cite web|title=Broadcasting Decision CRTC 2012-574|url=http://crtc.gc.ca/eng/archive/2012/2012-574.htm|publisher=CRTC|accessdate=18 October 2012|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112002612/http://crtc.gc.ca/eng/archive/2012/2012-574.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=gandm-crtcdenied>{{cite news|title=CRTC kills BCE-Astral merger deal|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/globe-investor/crtc-kills-bce-astral-merger-deal/article4621510/|publisher=The Globe and Mail|accessdate=18 October 2012|location=Toronto|date=18 October 2012|archive-date=2016-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160702035707/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/globe-investor/crtc-kills-bce-astral-merger-deal/article4621510/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在原有計劃下，貝爾收購星芒傳媒後會佔有加拿大英語電視市場的42%；在新建議下貝爾在該市場的份率則減至35.7%<ref name=cbc-compbureauok>{{cite news|title=Competition Bureau OK's BCE-Astral deal, with conditions|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2013/03/04/business-bell-astral-competition.html|publisher=CBC News|accessdate=5 March 2013|archive-date=2013-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130520043543/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2013/03/04/business-bell-astral-competition.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。交易於2013年3月18日獲加拿大競爭局許可<ref name=gandm-cbcorus>{{cite news|title=Competition Bureau clears Corus acquisition of Astral assets|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/competition-bureau-clears-corus-acquisition-of-astral-assets/article9886090/?cmpid=rss1|work=The Globe and Mail|publisher=Canadian Press|accessdate=20 March 2013|location=Toronto|date=18 March 2013}}</ref>，而CRTC於同年5月舉行聽證會後<ref name=gazette-bellresistant>{{cite web|title=Bell resistant to CRTC's TSN 690 proposal|url=http://www.montrealgazette.com/business/Bell+shoots+down+idea+selling+profitable+radio+station+keep/8345313/story.html|publisher=Montreal Gazette|accessdate=8 May 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508232611/http://www.montrealgazette.com/business/Bell%2Bshoots%2Bdown%2Bidea%2Bselling%2Bprofitable%2Bradio%2Bstation%2Bkeep/8345313/story.html|archivedate=2013年5月8日}}</ref>亦在6月27日有條件批准這項交易<ref name=torstar-approved>{{cite news|title=CRTC approves Bell/Astral deal with conditions|url=http://www.thestar.com/business/tech_news/2013/06/27/crtc_approves_bellastral_deal_with_conditions.html|work=Toronto Star|accessdate=5 July 2013|date=27 June 2013|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303062737/https://www.thestar.com/business/tech_news/2013/06/27/crtc_approves_bellastral_deal_with_conditions.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=cbc-astralapproved>{{cite news|title=CRTC approves Bell-Astral merger|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/business/story/2013/06/27/business-bell-astral-crtc-decision.html|work=CBC|accessdate=5 July 2013|archive-date=2013-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130827073723/http://www.cbc.ca/news/business/story/2013/06/27/business-bell-astral-crtc-decision.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

貝爾傳媒從2015年起展開裁員行動，11月6日在多倫多和蒙特婁裁減380個製作、編輯、銷售和行政職位<ref name=gandm-bmcuts>{{cite news|title=Bell Media to cut 270 jobs in Toronto, 110 in Montreal|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/bell-media-to-cut-jobs-in-toronto-montreal/article27130545/?|accessdate=22 November 2015|work=The Globe and Mail|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203085129/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/bell-media-to-cut-jobs-in-toronto-montreal/article27130545/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同月17日再於多倫多、溫哥華和渥太華的地區電視台和電台裁減包括幕前人員在内的職位<ref>{{cite news |last=Bateman |first=David |date=November 18, 2015 |title=Bell Media mass job cut affects TV personalities |url=http://www.thestar.com/business/2015/11/18/bell-media-mass-job-cut-affects-tv-personalities.html |newspaper=Toronto Star |location=Toronto, Canada |access-date=November 19, 2015 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206013226/https://www.thestar.com/business/2015/11/18/bell-media-mass-job-cut-affects-tv-personalities.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

康力斯娛樂於2015年11月宣佈將其位於加拿大西部的特級收費電視業務營運權以2億1100萬元轉售予貝爾傳媒，電影中心（{{lang|en|Movie Central}}）和[[安可道|安可道]]兩條頻道遂於2016年停播並由貝爾旗下的電影網絡（{{lang|en|The Movie Network}}）取代，而貝爾亦籍此成為加拿大國内唯一持有[[HBO|HBO]]節目播映權的公司<ref name=cbc-bellhbomc>{{cite news|title=Bell buys HBO rights across Canada as Corus backs out of pay TV|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/business/bell-buys-hbo-rights-across-canada-as-corus-backs-out-of-pay-tv-1.3328375|accessdate=22 November 2015|agency=Canadian Press|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108140102/https://www.cbc.ca/news/business/bell-buys-hbo-rights-across-canada-as-corus-backs-out-of-pay-tv-1.3328375|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

貝爾傳媒於2019年7月24日宣布從Remstar購入V電視網<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://montrealgazette.com/business/bell-media-set-to-add-quebec-tv-networks-with-v-network-purchase-to-roster|title=Bell Media set to add Quebec TV networks with V Média purchase|last=Tomesco|first=Frédéric|date=2019-07-24|access-date=2019-08-14|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206023317/https://montrealgazette.com/business/bell-media-set-to-add-quebec-tv-networks-with-v-network-purchase-to-roster|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該項交易於2020年4月3日獲CRTC批准<ref>{{cite web|url=https://crtc.gc.ca/eng/archive/2020/2020-116.htm|title=Broadcasting Decision CRTC 2020-116|publisher=[[加拿大視訊委員會|加拿大視訊委員會]]|date=2020-04-03|accessdate=2020-06-02|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805184154/https://crtc.gc.ca/eng/archive/2020/2020-116.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於同年5月15日落實<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/bell-welcomes-french-language-conventional-tv-network-v-and-noovo-ca-836940436.html|title=Bell's acquisition of V officially closes|work=Newswire Canada|date=May 15, 2020|accessdate=May 23, 2020|archive-date=2020-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200603015331/https://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/bell-welcomes-french-language-conventional-tv-network-v-and-noovo-ca-836940436.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，V電視網則於同年8月31日改稱「[[Noovo|Noovo]]」<ref name="cp-noovo-rename">{{cite web|url=https://www.lapresse.ca/arts/television/2020-08-19/la-chaine-v-deviendra-noovo.php|title=La chaîne V deviendra Noovo|author=The Canadian Press (uncredited staff)|work=La Presse|date=August 19, 2020|accessdate=August 19, 2020|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206162216/https://www.lapresse.ca/arts/television/2020-08-19/la-chaine-v-deviendra-noovo.php|dead-url=no}}{{fr}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://mediaincanada.com/2020/08/21/bell-media-brings-v-and-noovo-under-one-banner-rolls-out-campaign/|title=Bell Media brings V and Noovo under one banner, rolls out campaign|last=Summerfield|first=Patti|publisher=Media in Canada|date=2020-08-21|access-date=2020-10-07|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922071051/https://mediaincanada.com/2020/08/21/bell-media-brings-v-and-noovo-under-one-banner-rolls-out-campaign/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==資產==
貝爾傳媒的最大分部為貝爾傳媒電視（{{lang|en|Bell Media Television}}），旗下資產如下：

* [[CTV電視網|CTV電視網]]：加拿大規模最大、歷史最悠久和收視最高的私營英語免費[[電視網|電視網]]，包括其轄下全國21間直屬地區分台{{noteTag|name=O&O|1=CTV的21間直屬地區分台包括大西洋分台的四個地區訊號和北安大略分台的四個地區訊號，以及卡加利分台CFCN設於[[萊斯布里奇|列必珠]]的半轉播站，但不包括其他半轉播站。}}；
* [[CTV第二台|CTV第二台]]：次要[[電視系統|電視系統]]，包括其轄下7間直屬地區分台（當中5間為免費廣播，餘下2間則以收費電視接收）
* [[Noovo|Noovo]]：[[魁北克省|魁北克省]]法語電視網，包括其轄下5間直屬地區分台；
* {{link-en|特雷斯 (卑詩省)|Terrace, British Columbia|特雷斯}}{{link-en|CFTK-TV|CFTK-TV}}和[[道森克里克|道森克里克]]{{link-en|CJDC-TV|CJDC-TV}}：這兩間位於[[卑詩省|卑詩省]]的地區電視台原屬星芒傳媒，2013年落入貝爾傳媒控制，2016年起播放[[CTV第二台|CTV第二台]]節目，但保留原有的廣播品牌。

